<html>
<head>
    <%- include req %>
    <title>codeControl</title>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include header %>
    <div class = "centered container">
        <p>
        This is a JavaScript coding event as part of <em>codeControl</em> for <a href="//pragyan.org/">Pragyan</a>
        </p>
        <p>
        Visit the <a href = "/docs">Documentation</a>
        </p>
        <p>
        <% if(user) { %>
            Visit <%- link_to('your page', '/u/' + user.pid) %>
        <% } else { %>
            Start by <%- link_to('logging in', '/login') %>
        <% } %>
        </p>
        <p>
        You can challenge any character whose exp. difference with your character is less than 50.
        </p>
        <p>
        A character gets a fixed amount of exp. for every match won that decreases as he continues playing with the same player until finally getting no exp.
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
